{"id":1100,"date":"2021-10-28T23:10:09","date_gmt":"2021-10-28T16:10:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/?p=1100"},"modified":"2022-02-28T15:32:39","modified_gmt":"2022-02-28T08:32:39","slug":"xxxviii-disable-cfg-clock","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/10\/28\/xxxviii-disable-cfg-clock\/","title":{"rendered":"XXXVIII. Disable CFG-Clock"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_17 counter-hierarchy counter-decimal\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Danh m\u1ee5c<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><i class=\"ez-toc-glyphicon ez-toc-icon-toggle\"><\/i><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class=\"ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1\"><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/10\/28\/xxxviii-disable-cfg-clock\/#Cach_1_Disable_trong_config\" title=\"C\u00e1ch 1: Disable trong config \">C\u00e1ch 1: Disable trong config <\/a><\/li><li class=\"ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2\"><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/10\/28\/xxxviii-disable-cfg-clock\/#Cach_2_Dung_tool_grub-mod-setup\" title=\"C\u00e1ch 2: D\u00f9ng tool grub-mod-setup\">C\u00e1ch 2: D\u00f9ng tool grub-mod-setup<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_1_Disable_trong_config\"><\/span>C\u00e1ch 1: Disable trong config <span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t 1 \u00edt hi\u1ec7u n\u0103ng<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B1: m\u1edf config b\u0103ng <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/corpnewt\/ProperTree\">propertree<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B2: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n enable AppleCpuPmCfgLock v\u00e0 AppleXcpmCfgLock \u1edf ph\u1ea7n Kernel -&gt; Quirks<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cach_2_Dung_tool_grub-mod-setup\"><\/span>C\u00e1ch 2: D\u00f9ng tool grub-mod-setup<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B1: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n down tool <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/datasone\/grub-mod-setup_var\/releases\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B2: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n down uefitool <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/LongSoft\/UEFITool\/releases\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B3: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n down Universal-IFR-Extractor <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/LongSoft\/Universal-IFR-Extractor\/releases\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B4: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n down m\u00e3 bi bios c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ( c\u00e1i n mik kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n l\u00ean google search model + bin bios )<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B5: C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n k\u00e9o file bin bios v\u00e0o uefi tool sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea5n command + F <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>CFG Lock\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgur.com\/Wn0iuT4.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"\thttps:\/\/dortania.github.io\/OpenCore-Post-Install\/assets\/img\/uefi-tool.5f61054a.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B6: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n click chu\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o  setup v\u00e0 nh\u1ea5n <code>export as is<\/code> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgur.com\/gaOOJ8o.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>sau \u0111\u00f3 save d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1n <code>.bin<\/code> ho\u1eb7c <code>.sct<\/code><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B7: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edf terminal l\u00ean <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00e0 k\u00e9o file ifrextract \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u00ean v\u00e0o sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea5n d\u1ea5u c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c k\u00e9o file v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp theo b\u1ea1n g\u00f5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1eabn file txt mu\u1ed1n xu\u1ea5t vd <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><code>path\/to\/ifrextract path\/to\/Setup.bin path\/to\/Setup.txt<\/code><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgur.com\/rNX7OS4.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B8: sau \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf file v\u1eeba xu\u1ea5t l\u00ean v\u00e0 search <code>CFG Lock, VarStoreInfo (VarOffset\/VarName):<\/code>  \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm offset <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/imgur.com\/rN8cSzN.png\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 0x54<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B9: reboot v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn GRUB Shell sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f5 l\u1ec7nh <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>setup_var 0x5A4 \/\/ thay 0x54 th\u00e0nh offset b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>n\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i <code>error: offset is out of range<\/code> th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n g\u00f5 d\u00f2ng sau <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>setup_var2 0x5A4\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i <code>error: offset is out of range<\/code> th\u00ec c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n g\u00f5 d\u00f2ng sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>setup_var_3 0x5A4\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p l\u1ed7i \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n g\u00f5 l\u1ec7nh <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>setup_var_3 0x5A4 0x00\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>sau \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f5 <\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>reboot<\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<p>v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 xong b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eaft \u0111i <code>Kernel -> Quirks -> AppleCpuPmCfgLock<\/code>\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0<code>Kernel -> Quirks -> AppleXcpmCfgLock<\/code><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Source tham kh\u1ea3o: <a href=\"https:\/\/dortania.github.io\/OpenCore-Post-Install\/misc\/msr-lock.html#turning-off-cfg-lock-manually\">Fixing CFG Lock | OpenCore Post-Install (dortania.github.io)<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Danh m\u1ee5c C\u00e1ch 1: Disable trong config C\u00e1ch 2: D\u00f9ng tool grub-mod-setup C\u00e1ch 1: Disable trong config Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t 1 \u00edt hi\u1ec7u n\u0103ng B1: m\u1edf config b\u0103ng propertree B2: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n enable AppleCpuPmCfgLock v\u00e0 AppleXcpmCfgLock \u1edf ph\u1ea7n Kernel -&gt; Quirks C\u00e1ch 2: D\u00f9ng tool grub-mod-setup B1: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n down tool t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[48],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1100"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1100"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1100\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1105,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1100\/revisions\/1105"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1100"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1100"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1100"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}